06:31.782 --> 06:32.744
It's almost like you guys.

06:33.785 --> 06:44.080
Give it up your savings account or your retirement or your pension or even your week to week paycheck.

06:44.100 --> 06:45.142
That's how weighty that is.

06:47.125 --> 06:48.146
