To know Jesus is to know who he truly is, God in the flesh, the resurrection in the life, the one worthy of worship, and listen to this.

13:10.746 --> 13:18.418
To know Jesus is to know the deepest realities of who he is, what he gives, not just facts about him,

13:19.042 --> 13:23.910
